  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help 2,000 at-risk youth in Colombia build peace</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Solidarity Foundation in Medellin, Colombia will use its 29 years of experience to educate thousands of children and youths from the most at-risk locations in the city, literally showering them with warmth and love. The installations are first class, with teachers and psychologists on-site at every location. Furthermore, we offer shelter and counseling to several thousand additional at-risk adolescents; and all of this in the middle of gang-controlled poverty-stricken neighborhoods.</narrative>
  </description>
